data.description: 24 hr. notice to show  3-bed, 2-bath tri-level home featuring a spacious remodel kitchen with quartz countertops. Enjoy the luxury of a primary suite with a large walk-in closet and a master bath to dir for! First-floor laundry and a 2-car attached garage add convenience. Relax in the spacious great room with a gas fireplace or unwind in the 3-season room. The property boasts an inground pool, hot tub, fenced yard, and a generous patio overlooking the pool. This home is an entertainer's dream 1336 sq ft includes first and second floor 448 sq ft in the finished below grade. total sq ft. 1,784  Additional 200 sq ft in Three Season Room, not  included in overall sq. ft.  Appraisal completed 11/06/2023
